    "componentChunkName": "component---src-templates-post-template-js",
    "path": "/blog/2022-09-26-how-to-crop-only-one-layer-in-photopea/",
    "result": {"data":{"markdownRemark":{"excerpt":"Hello Friends üëã, Welcome To aGuidehub! ‚ù§Ô∏è To crop only one layer in photopea, right-click the layer and choose  and click on the . It will crop only one layer‚Ä¶","html":"<p>Hello Friends üëã,</p>\n<p>Welcome To aGuidehub! ‚ù§Ô∏è</p>\n<p>To crop only one layer in photopea, right-click the layer and choose <code class=\"language-text\">convert-to-smart-object</code> and click on the <code class=\"language-text\">crop tool</code>. It will crop only one layer of the image.</p>\n<p>Today, I am going to show you how I do crop only one layer in photopea.</p>\n<p><strong><em>There are two methods of cropping a single layer in photopea</em></strong></p>\n<p>Table of contents</p>\n<ul>\n<li>Insert images.</li>\n<li>Select the convert-to-smart-object.</li>\n<li>Select the smart-object-open.</li>\n<li>Choose the crop-tool.</li>\n<li>Save smart object.</li>\n</ul>\n<p>Let‚Äôs begin with our first method.</p>\n<h3>Method 1</h3>\n<h3>Step 1: Insert image.</h3>\n<p>Open the photopea and Select photo, it will open a <strong><em>file</em></strong> browser or download folder you can select the image. And click <strong><em>open</em></strong> button.</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 630px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/63c5e7c5db832a69aa1fae39539d7d64/38f6f/image.jpg\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 51.26582278481012%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"Photopea, image\"\n        title=\"Photopea, image\"\n        src=\"/static/63c5e7c5db832a69aa1fae39539d7d64/828fb/image.jpg\"\n        srcset=\"/static/63c5e7c5db832a69aa1fae39539d7d64/ff44c/image.jpg 158w,\n/static/63c5e7c5db832a69aa1fae39539d7d64/a6688/image.jpg 315w,\n/static/63c5e7c5db832a69aa1fae39539d7d64/828fb/image.jpg 630w,\n/static/63c5e7c5db832a69aa1fae39539d7d64/0ede0/image.jpg 945w,\n/static/63c5e7c5db832a69aa1fae39539d7d64/3ac88/image.jpg 1260w,\n/static/63c5e7c5db832a69aa1fae39539d7d64/38f6f/image.jpg 1366w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 630px) 100vw, 630px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<h3>Step 2: Select the convert-to-smart-object.</h3>\n<p>First, select your layer that you want to crop and convert it into smart-object by right click on the selective layer and it will give you a list of options select convert to smart object or Now open the smart-object layer by double click on the layer.</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 630px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/cbc740fc93ea74b2eb0a76c81033b2bb/38f6f/convert-to-smart-object.jpg\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 51.26582278481012%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"Photopea, convert-to-smart-object\"\n        title=\"Photopea, convert-to-smart-object\"\n        src=\"/static/cbc740fc93ea74b2eb0a76c81033b2bb/828fb/convert-to-smart-object.jpg\"\n        srcset=\"/static/cbc740fc93ea74b2eb0a76c81033b2bb/ff44c/convert-to-smart-object.jpg 158w,\n/static/cbc740fc93ea74b2eb0a76c81033b2bb/a6688/convert-to-smart-object.jpg 315w,\n/static/cbc740fc93ea74b2eb0a76c81033b2bb/828fb/convert-to-smart-object.jpg 630w,\n/static/cbc740fc93ea74b2eb0a76c81033b2bb/0ede0/convert-to-smart-object.jpg 945w,\n/static/cbc740fc93ea74b2eb0a76c81033b2bb/3ac88/convert-to-smart-object.jpg 1260w,\n/static/cbc740fc93ea74b2eb0a76c81033b2bb/38f6f/convert-to-smart-object.jpg 1366w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 630px) 100vw, 630px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<p>select your layer and then go to the layer from the menu select smart-object and then select convert to smart object.</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 630px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/2e6154dd2d7b2ada5d793a30cbb9a53c/10cbc/smart-object.jpg\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 53.79746835443038%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"Photopea, smart-object\"\n        title=\"Photopea, smart-object\"\n        src=\"/static/2e6154dd2d7b2ada5d793a30cbb9a53c/828fb/smart-object.jpg\"\n        srcset=\"/static/2e6154dd2d7b2ada5d793a30cbb9a53c/ff44c/smart-object.jpg 158w,\n/static/2e6154dd2d7b2ada5d793a30cbb9a53c/a6688/smart-object.jpg 315w,\n/static/2e6154dd2d7b2ada5d793a30cbb9a53c/828fb/smart-object.jpg 630w,\n/static/2e6154dd2d7b2ada5d793a30cbb9a53c/0ede0/smart-object.jpg 945w,\n/static/2e6154dd2d7b2ada5d793a30cbb9a53c/3ac88/smart-object.jpg 1260w,\n/static/2e6154dd2d7b2ada5d793a30cbb9a53c/10cbc/smart-object.jpg 1298w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 630px) 100vw, 630px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<h3>Step 3: Select the smart-object-open.</h3>\n<p>or go-to layer from the menu bar and select smart-object a drop-down menu will appear then select open.</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 630px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/5bd3f392ed7957d258f34cd0c751e186/38f6f/smart-object-open.jpg\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 50.632911392405056%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"Photopea, smart-object-open\"\n        title=\"Photopea, smart-object-open\"\n        src=\"/static/5bd3f392ed7957d258f34cd0c751e186/828fb/smart-object-open.jpg\"\n        srcset=\"/static/5bd3f392ed7957d258f34cd0c751e186/ff44c/smart-object-open.jpg 158w,\n/static/5bd3f392ed7957d258f34cd0c751e186/a6688/smart-object-open.jpg 315w,\n/static/5bd3f392ed7957d258f34cd0c751e186/828fb/smart-object-open.jpg 630w,\n/static/5bd3f392ed7957d258f34cd0c751e186/0ede0/smart-object-open.jpg 945w,\n/static/5bd3f392ed7957d258f34cd0c751e186/3ac88/smart-object-open.jpg 1260w,\n/static/5bd3f392ed7957d258f34cd0c751e186/38f6f/smart-object-open.jpg 1366w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 630px) 100vw, 630px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<p>now it will open a separate project..</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 630px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/f15f354c0118dfff2c5819835a096ed0/0c02e/background-psd.jpg\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 57.59493670886076%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"Photopea, background-psd\"\n        title=\"Photopea, background-psd\"\n        src=\"/static/f15f354c0118dfff2c5819835a096ed0/828fb/background-psd.jpg\"\n        srcset=\"/static/f15f354c0118dfff2c5819835a096ed0/ff44c/background-psd.jpg 158w,\n/static/f15f354c0118dfff2c5819835a096ed0/a6688/background-psd.jpg 315w,\n/static/f15f354c0118dfff2c5819835a096ed0/828fb/background-psd.jpg 630w,\n/static/f15f354c0118dfff2c5819835a096ed0/0ede0/background-psd.jpg 945w,\n/static/f15f354c0118dfff2c5819835a096ed0/0c02e/background-psd.jpg 1206w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 630px) 100vw, 630px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<h3>Step 4: Choose the crop-tool.</h3>\n<p>Now select crop tool from the toolbar or use shortcut press ‚Äòc‚Äô on your keyboard, now a grid will appear on your layer</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 630px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/c49cd2de584a14f6c6a13f5136d63dc4/38f6f/crop-tool.jpg\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 51.26582278481012%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"Photopea, crop-tool\"\n        title=\"Photopea, crop-tool\"\n        src=\"/static/c49cd2de584a14f6c6a13f5136d63dc4/828fb/crop-tool.jpg\"\n        srcset=\"/static/c49cd2de584a14f6c6a13f5136d63dc4/ff44c/crop-tool.jpg 158w,\n/static/c49cd2de584a14f6c6a13f5136d63dc4/a6688/crop-tool.jpg 315w,\n/static/c49cd2de584a14f6c6a13f5136d63dc4/828fb/crop-tool.jpg 630w,\n/static/c49cd2de584a14f6c6a13f5136d63dc4/0ede0/crop-tool.jpg 945w,\n/static/c49cd2de584a14f6c6a13f5136d63dc4/3ac88/crop-tool.jpg 1260w,\n/static/c49cd2de584a14f6c6a13f5136d63dc4/38f6f/crop-tool.jpg 1366w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 630px) 100vw, 630px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<p>now select one of his points and resize to an area you want to crop or select your layer then draw a rectangle to an area you want to crop and then press enter.</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 630px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/ad581108d49522bc69df4efe7b9b6a11/6fffd/press-enter.jpg\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 50.632911392405056%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"Photopea, press-enter\"\n        title=\"Photopea, press-enter\"\n        src=\"/static/ad581108d49522bc69df4efe7b9b6a11/828fb/press-enter.jpg\"\n        srcset=\"/static/ad581108d49522bc69df4efe7b9b6a11/ff44c/press-enter.jpg 158w,\n/static/ad581108d49522bc69df4efe7b9b6a11/a6688/press-enter.jpg 315w,\n/static/ad581108d49522bc69df4efe7b9b6a11/828fb/press-enter.jpg 630w,\n/static/ad581108d49522bc69df4efe7b9b6a11/0ede0/press-enter.jpg 945w,\n/static/ad581108d49522bc69df4efe7b9b6a11/3ac88/press-enter.jpg 1260w,\n/static/ad581108d49522bc69df4efe7b9b6a11/6fffd/press-enter.jpg 1364w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 630px) 100vw, 630px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<h3>Step 5: Save smart object.</h3>\n<p>Select the move tool and select file from the menu bar and then select save(smart-object) or press ‚Äòv‚Äô on your keyboard and then use shortcut press ‚Äòctrl+s‚Äô on your keyboard and it will save changes that we just made inside the smart-object layer. Now go back to your main project and you will see that your layer is now cropped not the whole project.</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 630px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/2d5a75fdd257e532632d1d9e06820562/38f6f/save-smart-object.jpg\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 50.632911392405056%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"Photopea, save-smart-object\"\n        title=\"Photopea, save-smart-object\"\n        src=\"/static/2d5a75fdd257e532632d1d9e06820562/828fb/save-smart-object.jpg\"\n        srcset=\"/static/2d5a75fdd257e532632d1d9e06820562/ff44c/save-smart-object.jpg 158w,\n/static/2d5a75fdd257e532632d1d9e06820562/a6688/save-smart-object.jpg 315w,\n/static/2d5a75fdd257e532632d1d9e06820562/828fb/save-smart-object.jpg 630w,\n/static/2d5a75fdd257e532632d1d9e06820562/0ede0/save-smart-object.jpg 945w,\n/static/2d5a75fdd257e532632d1d9e06820562/3ac88/save-smart-object.jpg 1260w,\n/static/2d5a75fdd257e532632d1d9e06820562/38f6f/save-smart-object.jpg 1366w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 630px) 100vw, 630px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<p>Final image.</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 630px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/b00f7d4bb92e6aaa1234d0b0cb5e3c20/e5081/final.jpg\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 51.26582278481012%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"Photopea, final\"\n        title=\"Photopea, final\"\n        src=\"/static/b00f7d4bb92e6aaa1234d0b0cb5e3c20/828fb/final.jpg\"\n        srcset=\"/static/b00f7d4bb92e6aaa1234d0b0cb5e3c20/ff44c/final.jpg 158w,\n/static/b00f7d4bb92e6aaa1234d0b0cb5e3c20/a6688/final.jpg 315w,\n/static/b00f7d4bb92e6aaa1234d0b0cb5e3c20/828fb/final.jpg 630w,\n/static/b00f7d4bb92e6aaa1234d0b0cb5e3c20/0ede0/final.jpg 945w,\n/static/b00f7d4bb92e6aaa1234d0b0cb5e3c20/3ac88/final.jpg 1260w,\n/static/b00f7d4bb92e6aaa1234d0b0cb5e3c20/e5081/final.jpg 1362w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 630px) 100vw, 630px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<h3>Method 2</h3>\n<p>This method is very simple than the first one selects the rectangle selection or use the keyboard shortcut ‚ÄòM‚Äô and hold left mouse click and draw to an area you want to crop and then.</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 630px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/fd27ca6a711a2cb352cea7fd7f7bd40e/902ab/rectangle-select.jpg\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 57.59493670886076%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"Photopea, rectangle-select\"\n        title=\"Photopea, rectangle-select\"\n        src=\"/static/fd27ca6a711a2cb352cea7fd7f7bd40e/828fb/rectangle-select.jpg\"\n        srcset=\"/static/fd27ca6a711a2cb352cea7fd7f7bd40e/ff44c/rectangle-select.jpg 158w,\n/static/fd27ca6a711a2cb352cea7fd7f7bd40e/a6688/rectangle-select.jpg 315w,\n/static/fd27ca6a711a2cb352cea7fd7f7bd40e/828fb/rectangle-select.jpg 630w,\n/static/fd27ca6a711a2cb352cea7fd7f7bd40e/0ede0/rectangle-select.jpg 945w,\n/static/fd27ca6a711a2cb352cea7fd7f7bd40e/902ab/rectangle-select.jpg 1204w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 630px) 100vw, 630px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<p>Go to the bottom right corner of the interface and select the add raster mask icon.</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 630px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/107f57b68bc7a5a0f200047dc7729da1/ff688/add-raster-mask.jpg\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 58.86075949367089%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"Photopea, add-raster-mask\"\n        title=\"Photopea, add-raster-mask\"\n        src=\"/static/107f57b68bc7a5a0f200047dc7729da1/828fb/add-raster-mask.jpg\"\n        srcset=\"/static/107f57b68bc7a5a0f200047dc7729da1/ff44c/add-raster-mask.jpg 158w,\n/static/107f57b68bc7a5a0f200047dc7729da1/a6688/add-raster-mask.jpg 315w,\n/static/107f57b68bc7a5a0f200047dc7729da1/828fb/add-raster-mask.jpg 630w,\n/static/107f57b68bc7a5a0f200047dc7729da1/0ede0/add-raster-mask.jpg 945w,\n/static/107f57b68bc7a5a0f200047dc7729da1/ff688/add-raster-mask.jpg 1226w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 630px) 100vw, 630px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<p>Now only that single layer is cropped that you selected earlier.</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 630px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/5447d7ab8ac54642ce7510cca9c97509/e4b8a/final-1.jpg\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 57.59493670886076%; position: relative; bottom